---
title: Rigatoni au Gratin with crispy breadcrumb topping
description: Rigatoni replaces macaroni in this elevation of a childhood favourite: mac and cheese. Luckily, the shape and structure of rigatoni make it the perfect vessel for the creamy, cheesy sauce that features in this recipe.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R09_W14_IE_IECFQVV13538-2_Main_high-3d923fe4.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/rigatoni-au-gratin-63b40657b1ab4b4b8a219512-d685dee2.pdf
